                <head>No. 147.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Pierrepont</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1876-11-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">November</hi> 30, 1876</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Fish</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Secretary, Washington:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Home office have ordered arrest of Winslow, Brent, and Gray.</p>
                <p>Winslow not here; disappeared early October. Brent here. Gray expected from
                    Paris.</p>
                <p>Foreign office prompt, careful j earnest to surrender.</p>
                <p>Will keep you advised.</p>
                <p rend="center">* * * * * * *</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>PIERREPONT.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
